{"id":249160,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-在京访民前往日本使馆举行游行抗议活动/","date":"2012-08-28T13:31:36Z","modified":"2012-08-28T13:31:36Z","title":"维权网 | 在京访民前往日本使馆举行游行抗议活动（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员关小令报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日上午</span><span>，各地在京访民前往日本大使馆门口举行具有示威抗议活动，打着“还我钓鱼岛”</span><span> </span><span>的横幅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时许，全国各地访民云集北京南站写示威抗议横幅时，马上招来警察的警觉，随后数名警察要求聚集的访民签名登记，有部分访民发现警方欲控制访民时，聚集的访民马上纷纷离开，据最后离开的访民说，她亲眼目睹警方抓了两位访民，其中一位是湖北省武汉市一位黄姓的访民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>被警方冲散的部分访民，仍然坚持前往日本驻中国大使馆去举行游行示威抗议活动，前去的访民有：湖南省长沙市访民刘友爱（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18975848285</span><span>）、林淑芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13121108649</span><span>）、湖南省益阳市访民陈月英（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13051768397</span><span>）、黄瑞连（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15210488318</span><span>）；湖北省十堰市访民王丽萍（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13972491436</span><span>）、周大珍（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13051390758</span><span>）、湖北省武穴市访民吴有明；辽宁省大连市访民赵明（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18604050516</span><span>）、辽宁省大石桥市访民邓承喜（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15941709396</span><span>）；浙江省杭州市访民应金仙；江苏省连云港市访民沈立秀（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15010913823</span><span>）、程学洪（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15010913823</span><span>）；陕西省宝鸡市吕动力（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13021151218</span><span>）；云南省梁河县访民江芳明（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13988206824</span><span>）、云南省永仁县访民罗志淑（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13187678967</span><span>）；江西省鹰潭市访民汪秀全（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18607018665</span><span>）、孙多平（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13970186935</span><span>）、周员兰（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13197800784</span><span>）、祖清山（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13197800784</span><span>）、江西省上饶市访民彭水保（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13340133276</span><span>）、万小桂（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13120123713</span><span>）、何爱兰（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13161931164</span><span>）、汪小琴（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13161931164</span><span>）、吴小英（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13426666382</span><span>）；重庆市访民刘修召（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18671633899</span><span>）。当访民队伍游行到距离日本大使馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>米</span><span>左右时被警方拦住，对参加游行的访民身份证逐一登记后，要求访民分成两批前往日本使馆前示威抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民的行动不仅仅是出于爱国方面的行动，更重要的是对当局的讽刺，很多访民多次向政府申请反腐游行示威，不仅不予批准，反而拘留打压，如此巨大反差，证明当局反腐是假。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民们说，为何日本侵占中国领土中国政府不敢回击，而对国内反腐民众大肆不择手段地镇压，实是不得民心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4cWTg3glVnE/UDyxwzZG93I/AAAAAAAAMZE/EilB9VsRQ-k/s1600/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E5%89%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"198\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4cWTg3glVnE/UDyxwzZG93I/AAAAAAAAMZE/EilB9VsRQ-k/s320/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E5%89%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>访民在日本使馆门口示威</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8FwIZG5uLOg/UDyx1iOeIcI/AAAAAAAAMZM/30ojrkObbJg/s1600/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"197\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8FwIZG5uLOg/UDyx1iOeIcI/AAAAAAAAMZM/30ojrkObbJg/s320/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1toGS8KsJTw/UDyx7DgZtYI/AAAAAAAAMZU/jfSYaU-YUtY/s1600/DSCF6269.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1toGS8KsJTw/UDyx7DgZtYI/AAAAAAAAMZU/jfSYaU-YUtY/s320/DSCF6269.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7146053323418507375?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}